{"id":13724,"name":null,"username":"Kobold","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/kobold/{size}/393_2.png","created_at":"2011-05-27T21:49:55.000Z","cooked":"<p>Because we havent written it down so far, heres the list of videos in VIDEO.HQR of LBA2. Sadly, theres no unused video like there was in LBA1. You will notice that the order of the movies is the same as when you view them in the memory viewer.</p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>1- ASCENSEU.SMK - Going down with the Elevator to the undergas<br>\n2- ASRETOUR.SMK - Going up with the Elevator to the undergas<br>\n3- BALDINO.SMK - Escaping from the Moon<br>\n4- BOAT1.SMK - Ferry: Fish scene<br>\n5- BOAT2.SMK - Ferry driving by<br>\n6- BOAT3.SMK - Ferry: drink scene<br>\n7- BOAT4.SMK - Ferry: esmer scene<br>\n8- BU.SMK - Temple of B ride<br>\n9- CRASH.SMK - Crash land on Twinsun<br>\n10- DARK.SMK - Dark Monks statue rises from the crater<br>\n11- DELUGE.SMK - Game Over<br>\n12- END.SMK - Ending<br>\n13- END2.SMK - Flying across the Hamalayi with Dino-Fly<br>\n14- ENFA.SMK - Childrens abduction<br>\n15- FRAGMENT.SMK - Wannies Fragment<br>\n16- GROTTE.SMK - Exiting Trals cave<br>\n17- INTRO.SMK - Intro<br>\n18- LUNES1.SMK - Moon approaches Twinsun<br>\n19- LUNES2.SMK - Moon flying from the side<br>\n20- MONTCH.SMK - Esmer shuttle starts from Bald Mountain<br>\n21- MOON.SMK - Moon Landing<br>\n22- PASSEUR.SMK - Ferryman ride<br>\n23- PUB1.SMK - Zeelich Presentation 1: Lab<br>\n24- PUB2.SMK - Zeelich Presentation 2: Parade<br>\n25- PUB3.SMK - Zeelich Presentation 3: Disco<br>\n26- PUB4A6.SMK - Zeelich Presentation 4: Last Ceremony<br>\n27- SENDELL.SMK - Ball of Sendell<br>\n28- SORT.SMK - Weather Wizard / Esmers arriving<br>\n29- SURSAUT.SMK - Emperor pulls the lever<br>\n30- TAXI.SMK - Leondine<br>\n31- TAXI_J.SMK - Hover Boat<br>\n32- VOYAGEZ.SMK - Shuttle passes by<br>\n33- ZEELP.SMK - Otringal Landing<br>\n34- BABY.SMK - Arthur</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Names retreived from Entry 49 of RESS.HQR</p>","post_number":1,"post_type":1,"posts_count":16,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T15:26:57.972Z","reply_count":13,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":9,"reads":1,"readers_count":0,"score":110.2,"yours":false,"topic_id":13721,"topic_slug":"lba-2-video-hqr-contents","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"bookmarked":false,"raw":"Because we haven't written it down so far, here's the list of videos in VIDEO.HQR of LBA2. Sadly, there's no unused video like there was in LBA1. You will notice that the order of the movies is the same as when you view them in the memory viewer.\n\n[quote]\n1- ASCENSEU.SMK - Going down with the Elevator to the undergas\n2- ASRETOUR.SMK - Going up with the Elevator to the undergas\n3- BALDINO.SMK - Escaping from the Moon\n4- BOAT1.SMK - Ferry: Fish scene\n5- BOAT2.SMK - Ferry driving by\n6- BOAT3.SMK - Ferry: drink scene\n7- BOAT4.SMK - Ferry: esmer scene\n8- BU.SMK - Temple of B ride\n9- CRASH.SMK - Crash land on Twinsun\n10- DARK.SMK - Dark Monk's statue rises from the crater\n11- DELUGE.SMK - Game Over\n12- END.SMK - Ending\n13- END2.SMK - Flying across the Hamalayi with Dino-Fly\n14- ENFA.SMK - Children's abduction\n15- FRAGMENT.SMK - Wannie's Fragment\n16- GROTTE.SMK - Exiting Tral's cave\n17- INTRO.SMK - Intro\n18- LUNES1.SMK - Moon approaches Twinsun\n19- LUNES2.SMK - Moon flying from the side\n20- MONTCH.SMK - Esmer shuttle starts from Bald Mountain\n21- MOON.SMK - Moon Landing\n22- PASSEUR.SMK - Ferryman ride\n23- PUB1.SMK - Zeelich Presentation 1: Lab\n24- PUB2.SMK - Zeelich Presentation 2: Parade\n25- PUB3.SMK - Zeelich Presentation 3: Disco\n26- PUB4A6.SMK - Zeelich Presentation 4: Last Ceremony\n27- SENDELL.SMK - Ball of Sendell\n28- SORT.SMK - Weather Wizard / Esmer's arriving\n29- SURSAUT.SMK - Emperor pulls the lever\n30- TAXI.SMK - Leondine\n31- TAXI_J.SMK - Hover Boat\n32- VOYAGEZ.SMK - Shuttle passes by\n33- ZEELP.SMK - Otringal Landing\n34- BABY.SMK - Arthur\n[/quote]\n\nNames retreived from Entry 49 of RESS.HQR","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":1918,"hidden":false,"trust_level":1,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba-2-video-hqr-contents/13721/1","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null,"can_vote":false}
{"id":365152,"name":"","username":"Polaris","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/polaris/{size}/28468_2.png","created_at":"2011-05-28T17:56:45.000Z","cooked":"<p>Have you noticed that the game over scene of LBA1 can be seen in that crystal globe, whereas LBA2s game over scene cant be seen in the memory viewer ?</p>","post_number":2,"post_type":1,"posts_count":16,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T18:47:46.495Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":1,"readers_count":0,"score":0.2,"yours":false,"topic_id":13721,"topic_slug":"lba-2-video-hqr-contents","display_username":"","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":"Hgsippe","title_is_group":false,"reply_to_user":{"id":1918,"username":"Kobold","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/kobold/{size}/393_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"Have you noticed that the game over scene of LBA1 can be seen in that crystal globe, whereas LBA2's game over scene can't be seen in the memory viewer ?","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":2162,"hidden":false,"trust_level":3,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba-2-video-hqr-contents/13721/2","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
