{"id":365156,"name":null,"username":"Kobold","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/kobold/{size}/393_2.png","created_at":"2011-05-28T18:09:58.000Z","cooked":"<p>You know, it just now occured to me that the list of videos is alphabetically ordered (except for the last one). So THATs why the videos in the memory viewer have this seemingly random order. Thats pretty bad design if you ask me. <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/stuck_out_tongue.png?v=12\" title=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>","post_number":5,"post_type":1,"posts_count":16,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T18:47:46.615Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":1,"readers_count":0,"score":0.2,"yours":false,"topic_id":13721,"topic_slug":"lba-2-video-hqr-contents","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":1918,"username":"Kobold","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/kobold/{size}/393_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"You know, it just now occured to me that the list of videos is alphabetically ordered (except for the last one). So THAT's why the videos in the memory viewer have this seemingly random order. That's pretty bad design if you ask me. :p","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":1918,"hidden":false,"trust_level":1,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":fal