{"id":365161,"name":"","username":"Polaris","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/polaris/{size}/28468_2.png","created_at":"2011-05-28T21:00:01.000Z","cooked":"<p>lol, agreed. That explains why the 2 end cinematics are in the middle of it. Is there such a list for LBA1 ? How are those cinematics ordered ?</p>","post_number":6,"post_type":1,"posts_count":16,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T18:47:46.783Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":1,"readers_count":0,"score":0.2,"yours":false,"topic_id":13721,"topic_slug":"lba-2-video-hqr-contents","display_username":"","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":"Hgsippe","title_is_group":false,"reply_to_user":{"id":1918,"username":"Kobold","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/kobold/{size}/393_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"lol, agreed. That explains why the 2 end cinematics are in the middle of it. Is there such a list for LBA1 ? How are those cinematics ordered ?","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":2162,"hidden":false,"trust_level":3,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba-2-video-hqr-contents/13721/6","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
{"id":365163,"name":null,"username":"Kobold","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/kobold/{size}/393_2.png","created_at":"2011-05-28T21:04:51.000Z","cooked":"<p>LBA 1 files are not stored in an HQR, but all in separate FLA files. I dont remember in which order they play, though if memory serves me right the intro was first.</p>\n<p>If you have LBAWin, you can find them in your /FLA/ folder. Use Alexfonts LBA Screen Viewer to watch them (without sound). Theres actually an unused video in there, a version of the video where Twinsen drops his clear water in front of the runic stone, but with different colors than in the actual game.</p>","post_number":7,"post_type":1,"posts_count":16,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T18:47:46.842Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":1,"readers_count":0,"score":0.2,"yours":false,"topic_id":13721,"topic_slug":"lba-2-video-hqr-contents","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":1918,"username":"Kobold","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/kobold/{size}/393_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"LBA 1 files are not stored in an HQR, but all in separate FLA files. I don't remember in which order they play, though if memory serves me right the intro was first.\n\nIf you have LBAWin, you can find them in your /FLA/ folder. Use Alexfont's LBA Screen Viewer to watch them (without sound). There's actually an unused video in there, a version of the video where Twinsen drops his clear water in front of the runic stone, but with different colors than in the actual game.","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":1918,"hidden":false,"trust_level":1,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba-2-video-hqr-contents/13721/7","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
