{"id":365897,"name":null,"username":"Zink","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/zink/{size}/61_2.png","created_at":"2011-07-15T13:57:47.000Z","cooked":"<p>Do you want to replace voices in VOX files, or voices in SMK videos?<br>\nIf the former, you posted your question in a wrong topic.</p>\n<p>Anyway, the voices probably must be the same sampling frequency and bit depth, as the originals (I dont remember now what they are, abut you can easily check that by unpacking an entry). I cant help you any further without knowing what steps you are taking exactly.</p>","post_number":14,"post_type":1,"posts_count":16,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T18:48:13.200Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":1,"readers_count":0,"score":5.2,"yours":false,"topic_id":13721,"topic_slug":"lba-2-video-hqr-contents","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":1918,"username":"Kobold","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/kobold/{size}/393_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"Do you want to replace voices in VOX files, or voices in SMK videos?\nIf the former, you posted your question in a wrong topic.\n\nAnyway, the voices probably must be the same sampling frequency and bit depth, as the originals (I don't remember now what they are, abut you can easily check that by unpacking an entry). I can't help you any further without knowing what steps you are taking exactly.","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":184,"hidden":false,"trust_level"